Command: status <message or "clear">
Argument: A string

The argument will be visible in your finger information,
or when someone tells you something, unless you have set
an away message, which precedes this. The message is also 
visible in your finger-information.

Example: status In sauna with Janina!
         status clear

See also 'away', 'tell'.

Command: status
Argument: none

Displays information about the gamedriver. 
Mainly relevant for the administrators.
